# Blog App Frontend

## Overview
Detailed explanation of frontend purpose and workflow.

## Features
- User Authentication
- Blog Viewing
- Create Blog
- Edit Blog
- Delete Blog
- Responsive UI
- Protected Routes
- API Integration

## Tech Stack
- React.js
- Vite
- JavaScript
- HTML5
- CSS3
- Axios
- React Router DOM
- Context API / State Management (if used)

## Frameworks and Libraries Used
| Tool | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| React | UI development |
| Vite | Fast frontend bundler |
| Axios | API requests |
| React Router | Client-side routing |
| CSS | Styling |

